organizations.name: viceland catch the premiere of 'twiz & tuck

text:
Catch the Premiere of 'TWIZ & TUCK' Tonight on VICELAND Two best friends—one gender fluid, the other trans—set out on a road trip to all the places that shaped them. 
Tonight on VICELAND, we'll be debuting the first episode of our series TWIZ & TUCK , which chronicles a road trip two best friends—one gender fluid, the other trans—take across America. Whether it's riding a bull in the Southwest or tearing it up in Vegas, Twiz and Tuck squeeze everything they can get out of each destination they visit. 
TWIZ & TUCK airs Mondays at 10:30 PM on VICELAND. 
Want to know if you get VICELAND? Head here to find out how to tune in.
